About https://secure.plaimi.net
===============================
This is the homepage of plaimi, a free software Haskell game development
company located in Gj√∏vik, Norway.

The Website is generated with Hakyll. We have chosen to make it publicly
available as an example Hakyll site to look at, for those of you who are
interested in learning Hakyll.

We accept patches. So if you think our page looks really ugly, just write a
patch that makes it beautiful. If you find a typo, clumsy HTML blocks,
anything -- you can report a bug at <https://secure.plaimi.net/bugs>, or fix
it yourself and send the patch to the mailing list:
<https://secure.plaimi.net/mailing.html>.


